{"tid":611702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解Facebook 貨不對辦詐騙案都仲咁多人中招？","createTime":"2018-03-31T09:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T11:11:26.000Z","uid":42407,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"340ad9cab7b4521ff3bdf6558cf2c610e5cdc463","tid":611702,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:47:47.000Z","msg":"【網購陷阱】一折無葉風扇貨不對辦逾200人受騙 速遞公司扣起貨款助苦主<br />\n<br />\n本港再出現網購陷阱！一個fb專頁早前號稱以1折的超抵價，以358元出售原價3,580元並聲稱來自英國的座地「無葉風扇」。專頁介紹風扇的功能，可送冷暖風及左右搖擺，更表明「貨到才收款」，限售100部，吸引數以百計的港人購買。豈料消費者近日從速遞員手上取貨及付款後，卻發現貨不對辦，他們所購得的，竟然是價值數十元的小型無葉風扇，更枉論冷暖風及搖擺功能，仿如玩具，懷疑有人欺詐及違反《商品說明條例》。有受害人向《蘋果》稱，已成立whatsapp群組討公道，估計苦主200至600人，涉款料逾10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180331/58017708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58017708&d=luiH7P9BE%2BiEfzh03p11%2FUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a4ee01ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58017708&h=8c501c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180331/58017708</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/174629_0886505c43b1b293a811c2f56befa213.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F174629_0886505c43b1b293a811c2f56befa213.png&h=bef4bf01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪就係因為你班窮撚又窮又貪心，無錢又學人用high class野，一折？用下腦啦傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"a7d3d4e12c0ff5fc942fd0b4cd16bdb9ce413eeb","tid":611702,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:50:55.000Z","msg":"窮人真係蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />